verses.text:
"We would see Je-sus:" for the shad-ows length-en A-cross the lit-tle landscape of our life;
We would see Je-sus: our weak faith to strength-en For the last weariness, the fi-nal strife.
We would see Je-sus: this is all we're need-ing, Strength, joy, and will-ing-ness come with the sight.
